<p><span>The Black Atlantic: Modernity and Double Consciousness[M]. London: Verso, 1993.</span></p>
<p><span>Between Camps: Nations, Cultures and the Allure of Race[M]. London: Allen Lane, Penguin Press, 2000. Also published as Against Race: Imagining Political Culture Beyond the Color Line[M]. Harvard University Press, 2000.</span></p>
<p><span>After Empire: Melancholia or Convivial Culture? [M]. London: Routledge, 2004. Also published as Postcolonial Melancholia[M]. New York: Columbia University Press, 2004.</span></p>
